headline: Gorman-Rupp (GRC) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Gorman-Rupp (GRC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +27.91% and +0.98%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
